              "text": {
                "type": "mrkdwn",
                "text": "*Learning Commands*\n`/learn` — Start or resume your current lesson\n`/learn <N>` — Jump to lesson number N\n`/submit <answer>` — Submit your answer for the current module\n`/progress` — View your learning progress across all courses\n`/courses` — Browse all available courses"
