            {
              "type": "section",
              "text": {
                "type": "mrkdwn",
                "text": "*Enrolment Commands*\n`/enroll <CODE>` — Enrol in a course using its code\n`/unenroll <CODE>` — Leave a course\n`/onboard` — Run the onboarding workflow (auto-enrols in OB courses)"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "section",
              "text": {
                "type": "mrkdwn",
                "text": "*Achievement Commands*\n`/cert` — Claim your certificate once all modules are complete\n`/report` — View a summary report of your team's learning\n`/gaps` — Identify skill gaps in your learning path"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "section",
              "text": {
                "type": "mrkdwn",
                "text": "*Admin Commands*\n`/backup` — Trigger a Google Sheets backup of all LMS data _(admin only)_"
